{"tid":2431800,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【Hello Kitty】真人版電影籌備兩年終開拍　由日裔巴西導演操刀","createTime":"2021-03-04T01:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:23:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"626aab75b98468e991111e6e205f0eb7baa6e17c","tid":2431800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"華納兄弟在2019年趁Hello Kitty誕辰45周年之際，宣布開拍真人版《Hello Kitty》電影。事隔差不多2年後，終於再有新消息。<br />\n<br />\n華納兄弟在2019年宣布旗下的新線影業（New Line Cinema）取得Hello Kitty的電影版權後，之後就再沒有傳出過新消息。近日外國傳媒《Deadline》報道，華納兄弟終於找到真人版《Hello Kitty》電影的導演人選。有指真人版電影的做法將會同《Tom &amp; Jerry大電影》（Tom and Jerry）一樣，是一部真人動畫電影。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指出，電視動畫《DC超級英雄女孩》美國女導演Jennifer Coyle將聯同短片《心腦交戰》日裔巴西導演松田李歐（Leo Matsuda）聯合執導；至於編劇方面，則由Lindsey Beer負責撰寫劇本。她近年獲得不少編劇機會，手上更有7個劇本需要處理，其中包括《狂野時速》全女班的外傳電影《M.A.S.K.: Mobile Armored Strike Kommand》。<br />\n<br />\n對於有幸獲邀成為真人版《Hello Kitty》電影導演，松田李歐認為他雖然在巴西長大，但同樣被Hello Kitty所吸引：「我與日本的家人在巴西長大，但我被與眾不同的Hello Kitty所包圍，這提醒我們可以有所不同。我好高興可以與Jennifer、Flynn Picture Company及新線影業一起開發這個全球最受歡迎的角色，並進一步擴充有關Hello Kitty的故事，這是一次難得的機會。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/443815315424415744563810.jpeg/pQU7I-8jaGRS6E9v9lhxGc2yBMtkPSyevBZOUbwWTlE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210303%2F443815315424415744563810.jpeg%2FpQU7I-8jaGRS6E9v9lhxGc2yBMtkPSyevBZOUbwWTlE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e0b3ae35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e70e478614a89dea0f5ae1859d59e8e6fe85b2e6","tid":2431800,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"係唔係要搵個無嘴既人拍?"},{"pid":"934128a1869d577459177a099d838363cf4ed418","tid":2431800,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e70e478614a89dea0f5ae1859d59e8e6fe85b2e6","tid":2431800,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"係唔係要搵個無嘴既人拍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"黑人"},{"pid":"06b8245ebfee868a3c76e63f373dc2d06bb52621","tid":2431800,"uid":19437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e70e478614a89dea0f5ae1859d59e8e6fe85b2e6","tid":2431800,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"係唔係要搵個無嘴既人拍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"要黑人做kitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a8e41e8e00e99ed7c46046987d5c6d0352a4e5","tid":2431800,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LiaYDPRedWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLiaYDPRedWQ&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=0f8b33d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LiaYDPRedWQ</a>"},{"pid":"5a8c3ec1e8f8e448d6f48fd5796c9038488fd4d5","tid":2431800,"uid":126100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"一諗真人 hello kitty 就諗到D 恐怖 hello kitty 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6eadf05fe7aad08dbd54401d9445fcc334ad2b","tid":2431800,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8c3ec1e8f8e448d6f48fd5796c9038488fd4d5","tid":2431800,"uid":126100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"一諗真人 hello kitty 就諗到D 恐怖 hello kitty 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"香港 hello kitty 人頭案 實在經典到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1578cbea3e8c1f31df4a13beae345fc2c59b0f7","tid":2431800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6eadf05fe7a